column8: Early morning fog in the outer suburbs. Mostly sunny. Light winds becoming north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h in the middle of the day.

Cloudy. The chance of fog in the southeast suburbs in the early morning. Medium (60%) chance of drizzle, most likely in the morning. Winds north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h tending southerly early in the morning then tending east to southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h in the late evening.

Partly cloudy. Patchy morning fog. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds northeast to southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light during the morning then becoming northwest to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the day.

Partly cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. Winds northerly 15 to 25 km/h increasing to 25 to 40 km/h during the morning then shifting south to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the evening.
Cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers. Winds southerly 15 to 25 km/h turning southeasterly during the day.
Partly cloudy. Patchy morning fog. High (70%) chance of showers. Winds northeast to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending southerly 20 to 30 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers. Winds southerly 25 to 35 km/h.
